{"actor":"Devon Jones","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-02-25T00:04:24Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":58,"issue_id":"PFSRD2-Parser-v90","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"PFSRD2-Parser-v90\",\"title\":\"Equipment parser: handle intelligent item stat blocks (41 items)\",\"description\":\"41 equipment items have intelligent item stat blocks separated by \\u003chr\\u003e tags that the parser doesn't handle. Pattern: after Usage/Bulk line, \\u003chr\\u003e introduces Perception, Communication, Skills, Int/Wis/Cha, Will fields, then another \\u003chr\\u003e before description. These are creature-like stat blocks that need new fields extracted into the JSON. IDs: 595, 596, 597, 618, 666, 1177-1180, 1590, 1725, 1743, 1748, 2376, 2382, 2392-2404, 2612, 3123, 3125-3127, 3750-3755, 3843, 4001\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"devon.jones@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-25T00:03:44Z\",\"created_by\":\"Devon Jones\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-25T00:03:44Z\"}"}
