{"actor":"Devon Jones","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-02-25T02:11:08Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":60,"issue_id":"PFSRD2-Parser-v89","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"PFSRD2-Parser-v89\",\"title\":\"Equipment parser: investigate Other HR-divided items (25 items)\",\"description\":\"25 equipment items have \\u003chr\\u003e-divided sections that don't match intelligent item or multi-stage patterns. Includes Aspects/Gifts (relics like Fan of the Four Winds), Covenants, Pacts, and other structures. IDs: 1546, 2405-2410, 2671, 2698, 2781, 3140-3146, 3452, 4016-4020, 4045-4046. Need to sub-categorize these and determine what fields/sections should be extracted.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"devon.jones@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-02-25T00:04:14Z\",\"created_by\":\"Devon Jones\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-25T00:04:14Z\"}"}
